<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Training Reminder</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #0A0A0A;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 0;
        }
        .page-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .urgency-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 14px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .urgency-high {
            background-color: #FEE2E2;
            color: #991B1B;
        }
        .urgency-medium {
            background-color: #FEF3C7;
            color: #92400E;
        }
        .urgency-low {
            background-color: #DCFCE7;
            color: #166534;
        }
        .training-info {
            background-color: #F5F5F5;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
        }
        .info-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-bottom: 0;
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #737373;
        }
        .info-value {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
        }
        .countdown-box {
            background-color: #171717;
            color: #FAFAFA;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .countdown-number {
            font-size: 40px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        .countdown-label {
            font-size: 13px;
            opacity: 0.75;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }
        .reminder-note {
            background-color: #FEF3C7;
            border: 1px solid #F59E0B;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #92400E;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
            color: #737373;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Employee Management System</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h1 class="page-title">Training Reminder</h1>

            {{#if (lt daysRemaining 2)}}
            <div><span class="urgency-badge urgency-high">Tomorrow</span></div>
            {{else if (lt daysRemaining 4)}}
            <div><span class="urgency-badge urgency-medium">In {{daysRemaining}} Days</span></div>
            {{else}}
            <div><span class="urgency-badge urgency-low">Upcoming</span></div>
            {{/if}}

            <p>Dear {{employeeName}},</p>

            <p>This is a reminder that you are enrolled in an upcoming training session. Please review the details below and make the necessary arrangements to attend.</p>

            <div class="training-info">
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Training:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{trainingName}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Date:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{trainingDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Time:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{trainingTime}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Location:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{location}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Instructor:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{instructor}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="countdown-box">
                <div class="countdown-number">{{daysRemaining}}</div>
                <div class="countdown-label">{{#if (eq daysRemaining 1)}}Day Remaining{{else}}Days Remaining{{/if}}</div>
            </div>

            <div class="reminder-note">
                <strong>Please note:</strong> Attendance is mandatory. If you are unable to attend due to an urgent reason, notify your manager and HR at least 24 hours in advance.
            </div>

            <p>If you have any questions about the training content or logistics, please reach out to your instructor or HR representative.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message from the Employee Management System.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
